@baseUrl = http://localhost:5142

### =========================================================================
### TAHAP 1: REGISTRASI & LOGIN USER BIASA (CUSTOMER)
### =========================================================================

### 1. REGISTER USER BARU (Budi)
# Secara otomatis sistem akan memberikan role "Customer" ke Budi
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Budi Santoso",
  "email": "budi@example.com",
  "password": "PasswordSuperAman123!",
  "phone": "081234567890"
}

###

### 2. LOGIN USER BUDI (Cek Role Awal)
# Perhatikan bagian "roles" di respon, seharusnya berisi: ["Customer"]
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "budi@example.com",
  "password": "PasswordSuperAman123!"
}


### =========================================================================
### TAHAP 2: AUTENTIKASI SUPER ADMIN (DATA SEEDING)
### =========================================================================

### 3. LOGIN SEBAGAI SUPER ADMIN
# Gunakan akun bawaan dari data seeding yang kita buat sebelumnya.
# Salin (Copy) string "token" yang muncul dari hasil respon ini untuk Tahap 3.
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "superadmin@ticket.com",
  "password": "AdminBesar123!"
}


### =========================================================================
### TAHAP 3: MANAJEMEN ROLE (ROLE-BASED ACCESS CONTROL)
### =========================================================================

### 4. SUPER ADMIN MENGUBAH ROLE BUDI MENJADI EVENT ORGANIZER
# Ganti 'ISI_TOKEN_SUPER_ADMIN_DI_SINI' dengan token yang didapat dari langkah nomor 3.
# Asumsi: ID si Budi di database adalah 2 (karena Super Admin adalah ID 1).
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/change-user-role
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJuYW1laWQiOiIxIiwidW5pcXVlX25hbWUiOiJTdXBlciBBZG1pbiBVdGFtYSIsImVtYWlsIjoic3VwZXJhZG1pbkB0aWNrZXQuY29tIiwicm9sZSI6IlN1cGVyQWRtaW4iLCJuYmYiOjE3ODM1MDI4NzAsImV4cCI6MTc4MzUwMzc3MCwiaWF0IjoxNzgzNTAyODcwLCJpc3MiOiJUaWNrZXRpbmcuQVBJIiwiYXVkIjoiVGlja2V0aW5nLkJsYXpvckNsaWVudCJ9.O89HjaW8WoGao4gTpDv0WeapuimxD6-jCDNQNmYKfrE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 2,
  "newRoleName": "EventOrganizer"
}

### =========================================================================
### TAHAP 4: VERIFIKASI PERUBAHAN
### =========================================================================

### 5. LOGIN ULANG USER BUDI (Verifikasi Role Baru)
# Jalankan ini setelah role diubah oleh Admin.
# Jika berhasil, bagian "roles" di respon sekarang akan berubah menjadi: ["EventOrganizer"]
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "budi@example.com",
  "password": "PasswordSuperAman123!"
}

### =========================================================================
### TAHAP 5: MANAJEMEN ORGANIZER (CRUD & VERIFIKASI)
### =========================================================================

### 6. EVENT ORGANIZER (Budi) MEMBUAT ORGANIZER BARU
# Gunakan Token hasil login BUDI (setelah rolenya berubah jadi EventOrganizer)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Organizer
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJuYW1laWQiOiIyIiwidW5pcXVlX25hbWUiOiJCdWRpIFNhbnRvc28iLCJlbWFpbCI6ImJ1ZGlAZXhhbXBsZS5jb20iLCJyb2xlIjoiRXZlbnRPcmdhbml6ZXIiLCJuYmYiOjE3ODM1MDI5MDMsImV4cCI6MTc4MzUwMzgwMywiaWF0IjoxNzgzNTAyOTAzLCJpc3MiOiJUaWNrZXRpbmcuQVBJIiwiYXVkIjoiVGlja2V0aW5nLkJsYXpvckNsaWVudCJ9.z8UYowKFHsGelzEZLBXI5xn4rT7dHU4N3H4QXb1xLJ8

{
  "ownerId": 2,
  "name": "Budi Jaya Entertainment",
  "description": "Organizer konser musik regional Sumatra.",
  "logoUrl": "https://linkgambar.com/logo-budi.png"
}

###

### 7. LIHAT SEMUA DAFTAR ORGANIZER (Akses Publik / Tanpa Token)
# Endpoint ini akan menampilkan seluruh organizer yang terdaftar di sistem
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Organizer

###

### 8. DETAIL ORGANIZER BERDASARKAN ID
# Asumsi: ID Organizer yang baru dibuat otomatis bernilai 1
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Organizer/1

###

### 9. SUPER ADMIN MEMVERIFIKASI DATA ORGANIZER
# Ganti 'TOKEN_SUPER_ADMIN_DI_SINI' dengan token dari langkah nomor 3.
# Status 'isVerified' akan diubah menjadi true agar organizer ini aktif secara legal di sistem
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/Organizer/1/verify
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJuYW1laWQiOiIxIiwidW5pcXVlX25hbWUiOiJTdXBlciBBZG1pbiBVdGFtYSIsImVtYWlsIjoic3VwZXJhZG1pbkB0aWNrZXQuY29tIiwicm9sZSI6IlN1cGVyQWRtaW4iLCJuYmYiOjE3ODM1MDI4NzAsImV4cCI6MTc4MzUwMzc3MCwiaWF0IjoxNzgzNTAyODcwLCJpc3MiOiJUaWNrZXRpbmcuQVBJIiwiYXVkIjoiVGlja2V0aW5nLkJsYXpvckNsaWVudCJ9.O89HjaW8WoGao4gTpDv0WeapuimxD6-jCDNQNmYKfrE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isVerified": true
}

###

### 10. EVENT ORGANIZER / SUPER ADMIN MEMPERBARUI DATA PROFIL ORGANIZER
# Pastikan Token yang digunakan memiliki role yang diizinkan di Controller Anda
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/Organizer/1
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJuYW1laWQiOiIxIiwidW5pcXVlX25hbWUiOiJTdXBlciBBZG1pbiBVdGFtYSIsImVtYWlsIjoic3VwZXJhZG1pbkB0aWNrZXQuY29tIiwicm9sZSI6IlN1cGVyQWRtaW4iLCJuYmYiOjE3ODM1MDI4NzAsImV4cCI6MTc4MzUwMzc3MCwiaWF0IjoxNzgzNTAyODcwLCJpc3MiOiJUaWNrZXRpbmcuQVBJIiwiYXVkIjoiVGlja2V0aW5nLkJsYXpvckNsaWVudCJ9.O89HjaW8WoGao4gTpDv0WeapuimxD6-jCDNQNmYKfrE

{
  "name": "Budi Jaya Entertainment - Updated",
  "description": "Organizer konser musik skala Nasional.",
  "logoUrl": "https://linkgambar.com/logo-budi-baru.png"
}

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
### =========================================================================
### TAHAP 6: MANAJEMEN STAFF ORGANIZER (DIBANTU OLEH EVENT ORGANIZER)
### =========================================================================

### 11. REGISTER USER BARU UNTUK CALON STAFF (Wati)
# Sebelum dimasukkan menjadi staff, user tersebut harus terdaftar di sistem terlebih dahulu
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Wati Setiawati",
  "email": "wati@example.com",
  "password": "PasswordStaff123!",
  "phone": "089876543210"
}

###

### 12. EVENT ORGANIZER (Budi) MENAMBAHKAN WATI SEBAGAI STAFF
# PENTING: Gunakan Token milik BUDI (EventOrganizer), karena Budi yang punya wewenang menambah staff
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Organizer/1/staffs
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJuYW1laWQiOiIyIiwidW5pcXVlX25hbWUiOiJCdWRpIFNhbnRvc28iLCJlbWFpbCI6ImJ1ZGlAZXhhbXBsZS5jb20iLCJyb2xlIjoiRXZlbnRPcmdhbml6ZXIiLCJuYmYiOjE3ODM1MDI5NzAsImV4cCI6MTc4MzUwMzg3MCwiaWF0IjoxNzgzNTAyOTcwLCJpc3MiOiJUaWNrZXRpbmcuQVBJIiwiYXVkIjoiVGlja2V0aW5nLkJsYXpvckNsaWVudCJ9.bwiRWf7v2tayOPHdSEkwRZwf6uIKm7fu7tcawph-bPQ

{
  "userId": 3,
  "position": "Ticketing Officer"
}

###

### 13. LIHAT DAFTAR STAFF DARI ORGANIZER TERCENTU
# Gunakan Token milik BUDI atau SUPER ADMIN
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Organizer/1/staffs
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJuYW1laWQiOiIxIiwidW5pcXVlX25hbWUiOiJTdXBlciBBZG1pbiBVdGFtYSIsImVtYWlsIjoic3VwZXJhZG1pbkB0aWNrZXQuY29tIiwicm9sZSI6IlN1cGVyQWRtaW4iLCJuYmYiOjE3ODM1MDI0NjMsImV4cCI6MTc4MzUwMzM2MywiaWF0IjoxNzgzNTAyNDYzLCJpc3MiOiJUaWNrZXRpbmcuQVBJIiwiYXVkIjoiVGlja2V0aW5nLkJsYXpvckNsaWVudCJ9.5QxKcSWV0BTZiBsljVMPgweAb0cjNCORnqO0e5QYfBI
###

### 14. EVENT ORGANIZER (Budi) MENGHAPUS STAFF DARI MANAJEMEN
# Gunakan Token milik BUDI
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/Organizer/1/staffs/1
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJuYW1laWQiOiIxIiwidW5pcXVlX25hbWUiOiJTdXBlciBBZG1pbiBVdGFtYSIsImVtYWlsIjoic3VwZXJhZG1pbkB0aWNrZXQuY29tIiwicm9sZSI6IlN1cGVyQWRtaW4iLCJuYmYiOjE3ODM1MDI0NjMsImV4cCI6MTc4MzUwMzM2MywiaWF0IjoxNzgzNTAyNDYzLCJpc3MiOiJUaWNrZXRpbmcuQVBJIiwiYXVkIjoiVGlja2V0aW5nLkJsYXpvckNsaWVudCJ9.5QxKcSWV0BTZiBsljVMPgweAb0cjNCORnqO0e5QYfBI

### =========================================================================
### TAHAP 7: MANAJEMEN EVENT (DIBUAT OLEH EVENT ORGANIZER)
### =========================================================================

### 15. EVENT ORGANIZER (Budi) MEMBUAT EVENT BARU
# Gunakan Token milik BUDI (EventOrganizer) yang didapat dari langkah verifikasi role.
# Asumsi: CategoryId 1 (misal: Kategori Konser) dan VenueId 1 (misal: Stadion) sudah tersedia di database (bisa melalui seeder).
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/events
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJuYW1laWQiOiIyIiwidW5pcXVlX25hbWUiOiJCdWRpIFNhbnRvc28iLCJlbWFpbCI6ImJ1ZGlAZXhhbXBsZS5jb20iLCJyb2xlIjoiRXZlbnRPcmdhbml6ZXIiLCJuYmYiOjE3ODM1Njg0OTIsImV4cCI6MTc4MzU2OTM5MiwiaWF0IjoxNzgzNTY4NDkyLCJpc3MiOiJUaWNrZXRpbmcuQVBJIiwiYXVkIjoiVGlja2V0aW5nLkJsYXpvckNsaWVudCJ9.rc6rie43Jl2wWmGyIZzGenTdjwFZB93WQADsbW9NG3I
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "organizerId": 1,
  "categoryId": 1,
  "venueId": 1,
  "title": "Konser Raya Sumatra 2026",
  "description": "Konser musik terbesar di Sumatra menampilkan artis-artis top ibu kota.",
  "posterUrl": "https://linkgambar.com/poster-konser-sumatra.png",
  "startTime": "2026-08-15T19:00:00Z",
  "endTime": "2026-08-15T23:30:00Z",
  "status": "draft"
}

###

### 16. EVENT ORGANIZER (Budi) MEMBUAT EVENT DENGAN VALIDASI GAGAL (TESTING)
# Menguji validasi: EndTime dibuat lebih awal dari StartTime. Harus mengembalikan 400 BadRequest.
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/events
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJuYW1laWQiOiIyIiwidW5pcXVlX25hbWUiOiJCdWRpIFNhbnRvc28iLCJlbWFpbCI6ImJ1ZGlAZXhhbXBsZS5jb20iLCJyb2xlIjoiRXZlbnRPcmdhbml6ZXIiLCJuYmYiOjE3ODM1Njg0OTIsImV4cCI6MTc4MzU2OTM5MiwiaWF0IjoxNzgzNTY4NDkyLCJpc3MiOiJUaWNrZXRpbmcuQVBJIiwiYXVkIjoiVGlja2V0aW5nLkJsYXpvckNsaWVudCJ9.rc6rie43Jl2wWmGyIZzGenTdjwFZB93WQADsbW9NG3I
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "organizerId": 1,
  "categoryId": 1,
  "venueId": 1,
  "title": "Event Salah Jadwal",
  "description": "Contoh event dengan validasi jadwal gagal.",
  "startTime": "2025-08-15T19:00:00Z",
  "endTime": "2026-08-10T23:30:00Z", 
  "status": "draft"
}

###

### 17. LIHAT DETAIL EVENT BERDASARKAN ID
# Endpoint ini bersifat publik (tanpa token) untuk menampilkan detail event ke calon pembeli tiket.
# Asumsi: ID Event yang sukses dibuat pada langkah nomor 15 otomatis bernilai 1.
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events/7

###

### =========================================================================
### TAHAP 8: MANAJEMEN TIKET (TICKET TYPES & STOCK)
### =========================================================================

### 18. EVENT ORGANIZER (Budi) MEMBUAT JENIS TIKET FESTIVAL (TANPA KURSI)
# Endpoint untuk membuat tipe tiket Festival (IsNumberedSeat = false).
# Logic di Service akan otomatis membuat TicketStock dengan AvailableStock 1000.
# Catatan: Asumsi EventId yang digunakan adalah 7 (sesuai URL Get Event di tahap sebelumnya).
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/events/7/ticket-types
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJuYW1laWQiOiIyIiwidW5pcXVlX25hbWUiOiJCdWRpIFNhbnRvc28iLCJlbWFpbCI6ImJ1ZGlAZXhhbXBsZS5jb20iLCJyb2xlIjoiRXZlbnRPcmdhbml6ZXIiLCJuYmYiOjE3ODM1Njg0OTIsImV4cCI6MTc4MzU2OTM5MiwiaWF0IjoxNzgzNTY4NDkyLCJpc3MiOiJUaWNrZXRpbmcuQVBJIiwiYXVkIjoiVGlja2V0aW5nLkJsYXpvckNsaWVudCJ9.rc6rie43Jl2wWmGyIZzGenTdjwFZB93WQADsbW9NG3I
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": 7,
  "name": "Festival (Standing)",
  "description": "Area standing di depan panggung utama.",
  "price": 500000,
  "totalQuota": 1000,
  "startSales": "2026-07-15T09:00:00Z",
  "endSales": "2026-08-14T23:59:59Z",
  "isNumberedSeat": false
}

###

### 19. EVENT ORGANIZER (Budi) MEMBUAT JENIS TIKET VIP (NUMBERED SEAT)
# Endpoint untuk membuat tipe tiket VIP (IsNumberedSeat = true).
# Akan digunakan nanti sebagai dasar pembentukan SeatMap dan Seat.
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/events/7/ticket-types
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJuYW1laWQiOiIyIiwidW5pcXVlX25hbWUiOiJCdWRpIFNhbnRvc28iLCJlbWFpbCI6ImJ1ZGlAZXhhbXBsZS5jb20iLCJyb2xlIjoiRXZlbnRPcmdhbml6ZXIiLCJuYmYiOjE3ODM1Njg0OTIsImV4cCI6MTc4MzU2OTM5MiwiaWF0IjoxNzgzNTY4NDkyLCJpc3MiOiJUaWNrZXRpbmcuQVBJIiwiYXVkIjoiVGlja2V0aW5nLkJsYXpvckNsaWVudCJ9.rc6rie43Jl2wWmGyIZzGenTdjwFZB93WQADsbW9NG3I
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": 7,
  "name": "VIP",
  "description": "Area duduk eksklusif dengan nomor kursi (Seat Plan).",
  "price": 1500000,
  "totalQuota": 100,
  "startSales": "2026-07-15T09:00:00Z",
  "endSales": "2026-08-14T23:59:59Z",
  "isNumberedSeat": true
}

###

### 20. EVENT ORGANIZER MEMBUAT TIKET DENGAN VALIDASI GAGAL (TESTING)
# Menguji validasi keamanan di Controller: eventId di URL (7) tidak cocok dengan eventId di Body Request (99).
# Harus mengembalikan status 400 BadRequest.
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/events/7/ticket-types
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJuYW1laWQiOiIyIiwidW5pcXVlX25hbWUiOiJCdWRpIFNhbnRvc28iLCJlbWFpbCI6ImJ1ZGlAZXhhbXBsZS5jb20iLCJyb2xlIjoiRXZlbnRPcmdhbml6ZXIiLCJuYmYiOjE3ODM1Njg0OTIsImV4cCI6MTc4MzU2OTM5MiwiaWF0IjoxNzgzNTY4NDkyLCJpc3MiOiJUaWNrZXRpbmcuQVBJIiwiYXVkIjoiVGlja2V0aW5nLkJsYXpvckNsaWVudCJ9.rc6rie43Jl2wWmGyIZzGenTdjwFZB93WQADsbW9NG3I
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": 7,
  "name": "Reguler Salah ID",
  "description": "Validasi gagal karena ID di Body berbeda dengan URL.",
  "price": 200000,
  "totalQuota": 500,
  "startSales": "2026-07-15T09:00:00Z",
  "endSales": "2026-08-14T23:59:59Z",
  "isNumberedSeat": false
}

###

### 21. PELANGGAN MELIHAT DAFTAR JENIS TIKET BERDASARKAN EVENT ID
# Endpoint publik (tanpa token) untuk melihat jenis tiket apa saja yang tersedia di Event ID 7.
# Response akan mengembalikan list TicketType lengkap dengan AvailableStock dari TicketStock.
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events/7/ticket-types

###

### =========================================================================
### TAHAP 9: PUBLIKASI EVENT
### =========================================================================

### 22. EVENT ORGANIZER (Budi) MEMPUBLIKASIKAN EVENT
# Endpoint untuk mengubah status event dari 'draft' menjadi 'published'.
# Memerlukan token Authorization dari Organizer (Budi).
# EventId yang digunakan adalah 7.

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/events/7/publish
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJuYW1laWQiOiIyIiwidW5pcXVlX25hbWUiOiJCdWRpIFNhbnRvc28iLCJlbWFpbCI6ImJ1ZGlAZXhhbXBsZS5jb20iLCJyb2xlIjoiRXZlbnRPcmdhbml6ZXIiLCJuYmYiOjE3ODM1NzM2ODQsImV4cCI6MTc4MzU3NDU4NCwiaWF0IjoxNzgzNTczNjg0LCJpc3MiOiJUaWNrZXRpbmcuQVBJIiwiYXVkIjoiVGlja2V0aW5nLkJsYXpvckNsaWVudCJ9.9-Tmdxa5rM7f-JyTzGvj98GjIF3QoBTqdwY5AwdZN40
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "notes": "Event Festival Musik 2026 siap dimulai, tiket sudah tersedia untuk dibeli."
}

### 23. VERIFIKASI HASIL PUBLIKASI (GET EVENT)
# Mengecek apakah status event sudah berubah menjadi 'published'.
# Asumsi Anda sudah memiliki endpoint GET /api/events/{id}

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events/7
Content-Type: application/json